- author: matthew
  body: Well, i guess this is personal taste.  I quite like the IRC idiom that the text box is for both commands and text, and just because you're not currently in a room doesn't mean that CLI should be disabled and you should be forced to use the GUI.  We want the reference apps to be familiar to IRC users, so I personally think we should fix this (at low priority).
